te":{"pid":"9345a0e7fd9b226ddbeaf107d333de223487f90f","tid":1905820,"uid":265932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"試過兩次喺外國行山<br />\n一座4千幾，一座3千幾米<br />\nEnjoy~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"邊2座 好鐘意行外國山 依加去旅行 首先會搵邊到有山行先  如果搵唔到可能會轉第二個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"Abc, 同埋 林賈尼<br />\n同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398d08d0b3463525e74c786ae9ece511e5e53a40","tid":1905820,"uid":272614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"試過一條友行咗4日麥徑全走同3日鳳凰徑全走"},{"pid":"7a8f7dd2b95f875f55463018f901027de130411b","tid":1905820,"uid":23271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef71bb0e05f69d2af55a3a1b85481d5af210a5a6","tid":1905820,"uid":12623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"自己單拖行咗兩年幾<br />\n三年幾前入咗個行山谷正式行山<br />\n初頭要有人陪先行<br />\n但因為好難約時間所以慢慢開始自己行<br />\n因為我覺得行四大徑 啲公廁山好悶好冇引<br />\n一行就會上網搵啲刺激路線行下 愈行愈過癮<br />\n最近衝破心理關口自己單拖行彌天棧道上象額<br />\n希望來生可以單拖行到東西馬肚 / 行螺旋壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T17:59:38.000Z","msg":"真正嘅行山<br />\n摸路同手腳技巧 係重要過體能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39078ec7af6ce58bd537efcd8de88565d065c44","tid":1905820,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cab10547cf5717bf394a4cd40f41ae273e64b3b","tid":1905820,"uid":157865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:47:06.000Z","msg":"試過一個人去紐西蘭行山,好爽,不過真係要操好D先好行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c872a11812203a863e521c59b8a0de7dc3b82b","tid":1905820,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"原來好多巴絲打都中意一個人行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d966a1167517ab91ab00a14c69a3b6842be0b483","tid":1905820,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7bb2ebe086ab7482f34481bbca034154b8ff4d6","tid":1905820,"uid":278645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"其實喺香港, 四大徑平日都超多人行, 連夜晚都有人行, 唔駛點擔心一個人出事冇人救, 同埋其實真係冇幾多路段可以跌死你, 新聞嗰啲好多都係啲行澗, 爬山級, 高危路線, 你正正常常行大路唔會去咗嗰啲<br />\n反思, 思考人生呀嗰啲冇乜試過, 行山本身就係一種享受, 唔鬼想諗啲乜Q嘢."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"邊4大"},{"pid":"684c8418804c5f888071bc41d08ccc998d1b4097","tid":1905820,"uid":152061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"試過幾年前自己去大阪金剛山<br />\n果陣二月黎市區無雪，但原來上到山頂仲有好多積雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果朝又自己ON9剩係食左早餐唔記得買飯團上山食剩係帶左水<br />\n諗住有排餓落番市區先有野食, 點知有個婆唔婆知係咪見我一個毒撚走埋搵我吹水, 本身有學過日文所以都同佢傾到下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傾傾下佢比左舊唔知無花果乾定柿乾我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢道別之後喺山頂行多陣原來另一邊有杯麵機, 即刻買番個黎食 暖哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋影金剛山幾多米高個牌打卡果陣有大叔主動問洗唔洗幫我同個牌影相<br />\n沿途行既時候迎面而來既人又會打招呼, 仲有樣最欣賞既係由上山到落山四周圍真係一舊垃圾都無<br />\n果次獨行真係充分感受到日本人既友善同公德心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺香港間中都有獨行對上一次去大刀屻<br />\n<br />\n自己一定做足功課睇定地圖邊到落邊到上,唔行小路<br />\n裝番個地圖APP睇自己行到邊, 順便記錄下自己要行幾耐同行到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1efdfcf444366e2a4b59fb0c6247fbbaf013bc4","tid":1905820,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"成日單拖操針草帽"},{"pid":"58bfad14f0b5ba19061459dcfc2bf06fd9a6adff","tid":1905820,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aebb7e04609bd22578ca8a3be826f76982834fe","tid":1905820,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a64789f39f90b00bc157e11c274c381d565aa6b","tid":1905820,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"行山係唔應該一個人行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"好多單出事都係一個人...<br />\n小新作者"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:21:57.000Z","msg":"我細個學行山都話行山最少要三個人<br />\n唔係話你會蕩失路，你山入面整親腳，行唔到眼望唔到標矩柱，邊個救到你?"},{"pid":"e2b737fa393f9354e0d6e001308ea420417f7a8b","tid":1905820,"uid":133652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bfad14f0b5ba19061459dcfc2bf06fd9a6adff","tid":1905820,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aebb7e04609bd22578ca8a3be826f76982834fe","tid":1905820,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a64789f39f90b00bc157e11c274c381d565aa6b","tid":1905820,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"行山係唔應該一個人行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"好多單出事都係一個人...<br />\n小新作者"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:21:57.000Z","msg":"我細個學行山都話行山最少要三個人<br />\n唔係話你會蕩失路，你山入面整親腳，行唔到眼望唔到標矩柱，邊個救到你?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"咁而家有GPS就方便過以前嘅<br />\n行山徑有晒標距柱<br />\n我自己一個行會Send SMS去政府到"},{"pid":"a5fd4cea3d491759b4ccf782dd5afcb2ab231877","tid":1905820,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b737fa393f9354e0d6e001308ea420417f7a8b","tid":1905820,"uid":133652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bfad14f0b5ba19061459dcfc2bf06fd9a6adff","tid":1905820,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aebb7e04609bd22578ca8a3be826f76982834fe","tid":1905820,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"好多單出事都係一個人...<b